videos.description: Lebron James says he did not play well tonight in both halves which is why he switched his shoes.

videos.headline: LeBron on shoe change: 'If there was a 3rd half, I'd take those off too'

videos.description: In D.C., LeBron James dons one white sneaker and one black sneaker with the word "equality" displayed. After the Cavaliers' win over the Wizards, James shares why he chose to wear the shoes.
